        <IRI>#trafficDensity</IRI>
        <Literal>Property that points out the number of vehicles  occupying a section of roadway (highway, carriageway, or lane) per unit of length at a given moment. It is a key congestion indicator that reduces speed.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
    <AnnotationAssertion>
        <AnnotationProperty abbreviatedIRI="rdfs:comment"/>
